target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Rocky%20Mountains%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sit%20on%20the%20left%20side.%20However%2C%20the%20right%20side%20is%20better%20if%20you%20prefer%20being%20close%20to%20the%20Colorado%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhichever%20side%20you%20pick%2C%20you%20can%20always%20go%20to%20the%20observation%20car%20for%20even%20better%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20observation%20car%20fills%20up%20quickly%2C%20but%20you%20can%20find%20great%20views%20just%20below%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crowded%20observation%20car%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6324c9b67a2f62001868f2db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20found%20equally%20pretty%20views%20under%20the%20observation%20car%20and%20avoided%20the%20crowds.%3Cp%3EDiana%20Kruzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20the%20observation%20car%20during%20the%20most%20scenic%20stretches%20of%20the%20Zephyr's%20route%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20through%20the%20Rocky%20Mountains%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20it%C2%A0tricky%20to%20find%20a%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20full%2C%20head%20to%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car%2C%20which%20is%20right%20below%20the%20observation%20deck%20on%20the%20Zephyr.%20There%20are%20tables%20right%20up%20against%20the%20large%20windows%2C%20and%20you'll%20have%20almost%20as%20good%20a%20view%20as%20you'd%20get%20upstairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20buy%20something%20to%20sit%20there%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20worth%20it%20for%20a%20change%20of%20scenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20no%20WiFi%20on%20certain%20Amtrak%20routes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20when%20there%20is%2C%20it%20can%20be%20spotty.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22person%20holding%20a%20book%20open%20while%20riding%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6324c8d17a2f62001868f279%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20made%20sure%20to%20bring%20a%20book%20on%20the%20train.%3Cp%3EDiana%20Kruzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20Zephyr%20didn't%20have%20WiFi%20on%20board%2C%20and%20cell%20service%20was%20poor%20or%20nonexistent%20going%20through%20the%20Sierra%20Nevada%20mountains%20and%20parts%20of%20Nevada%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20Nebraska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I'd%20downloaded%20some%20movies%20and%20reading%20materials%20in%20advance%2C%20which%20helped%20pass%20the%20time%20when%20I%20couldn't%20use%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20you%20can%20reliably%20work%20remotely%20from%20the%20train.%20Even%20when%20I%20was%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-on-long-train-ride-from-dc-to-chicago-photos-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECardinal%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20WiFi%2C%20I%20found%20the%20service%20cut%20in%20and%20out%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20can%20get%20cold%20on%20the%20train%2C%20so%20remember%20to%20bring%20a%20jacket%20and%20comfortable%20clothes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22diana%20wearing%20a%20jacket%20while%20riding%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6324c945a6c3e8001966a201%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20got%20chilly%20on%20my%20trains.%3Cp%3EDiana%20Kruzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20the%20train%20cars%20are%20air-conditioned%20in%20the%20summer.%20However%2C%20that%20can%20also%20make%20them%20quite%20chilly%2C%20especially%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20came%20prepared%20for%20my%20rides%20with%20some%20thermal%20leggings%20and%20a%20puffy%20jacket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20to%20wear%20clothes%20that%20you're%20comfortable%20sitting%20in%20for%20extended%20periods.%20I%20also%20recommend%20bringing%20a%20change%20of%20clothes%20(or%20at%20least%20an%20extra%20shirt)%20if%20you're%20traveling%20for%20multiple%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBring%20snacks%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20options%20in%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221511%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20holding%20a%20bag%20of%20nuts%20and%20a%20clementine%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6324ca167a2f62001868f2f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20brought%20some%20food%20to%20eat%20on%20my%20long%20journey.%3Cp%3EDiana%20Kruzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stopped%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-nutritionist-buys-at-trader-joes-for-2-people-list-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrader%20Joe's%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20my%20trip%20and%20came%20fully%20loaded%20with%20some%20granola%20bars%2C%20clementines%2C%20and%20pita%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20haul%20kept%20me%20from%20being%20too%20hungry%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-food-review-cafe-car-menu-prices-photos-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20caf%C3%A9%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20ran%20out%20of%20everything%20I%20wanted%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20were%20vegetarian%20options%20on%20the%20train%2C%20if%20you're%20vegan%20or%20have%20any%20special%20dietary%20needs%20or%20allergies%2C%20it's%20probably%20best%20to%20bring%20some%20of%20your%20own%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20possible%20to%20get%20free%20hot%20water%20on%20the%20trains.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22someone%20standing%20in%20the%20cafe%20car%20area%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6324ccb37a2f62001868f45a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20people%20brought%20%26quot%3Bjust%20add%20water%26quot%3B%20meals%20on%20the%20train.%3Cp%3EDiana%20Kruzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20on%20this%20journey%20that%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car%20had%20a%20supply%20of%20free%20hot%20water.%20You%20can%20bring%20your%20own%20food%2C%20like%20a%20cup%20of%20instant%20noodles%2C%20or%20tea%2C%20and%20just%20ask%20a%20staff%20member%20to%20fill%20up%20your%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20several%20passengers%20doing%20this%20and%20wished%20I'd%20thought%20to%20bring%20some%20just-add-water%20meals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20spigots%20dispensing%20drinking%20water%20throughout%20the%20train%2C%20though%20they%20were%20pretty%20slow%20to%20use.%20I%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20buying%20bottled%20water%2C%20so%20I%20made%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBring%20a%20pillow%20and%20a%20blanket%20to%20make%20sleeping%20more%20comfortable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22big%20pillow%20sitting%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6324cd85a6c3e8001966a3af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20glad%20I%20brought%20a%20comfortable%20pillow.%3Cp%3EDiana%20Kruzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20seats%20leaned%20back%20and%20had%20a%20leg%20rest%20that%20extended%20outward%2C%20making%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20sleep%20than%20on%20a%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20a%20pillow%20is%20essential%20%E2%80%94%20either%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-i-packed-on-20-hour-train-ride-amtrak-photos-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20pillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20you%20can%20use%20to%20sleep%20upright%20or%20a%20standard%20one%20that%20you%20can%20lean