%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-big-four-hire-tech-talent-ai-workplace-transformation-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elooking%20for%20hundreds%20and%20hundreds%20of%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohamed%20Kande%2C%20the%20firm's%20global%20chairman%2C%20told%20the%20BBC%20in%20November.%20The%20firm%20has%20created%20an%20engineering%20career%20path%20to%20%26quot%3Belevate%20engineering%20excellence%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20firm%20and%20expand%20opportunities%20for%20technical%20talent%2C%20PwC%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpskilling%20has%20also%20become%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20the%20Big%20Four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20EY%20rolled%20out%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20its%20employees%20that%20helps%20them%20identify%20how%20their%20jobs%20will%20change%E2%80%A6%20because%20of%20AI.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20help%20them%20work%20out%20how%20they%20can%20better%20use%20the%20technology%20in%20their%20current%20job%20and%20adapt%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20100%2C000%20EY%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20workforce%20%E2%80%94%20have%20also%20earned%20a%20digital%20%26quot%3BAI%20badge%26quot%3B%20for%20completing%20one%20of%20the%20firm's%20new%20AI%20learning%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Business%20Insider%20learned%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-ai-training-how-companies-are-teaching-employees-to-use-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esitting%20in%20on%20a%20KPMG's%20AI%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20tax%20interns%2C%20in%20professional%20services%2C%20some%20of%20AI's%20most%20effective%20uses%20hinge%20on%20strong%20prompting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KPMG%20Lakehouse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69441453832e0ef1ead67751%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKPMG%20t