%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20conversation%20with%20a%20top%20Amazon%20seller%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whom%20we%20consulted%20in%20the%20ideation%20stage.%20He%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20about%20our%20interests%20and%20how%20we%20generally%20spend%20our%20time.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20like%3F%20What%20are%20you%20good%20at%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20us.%20%26quot%3BStart%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20former%20collegiate%20tennis%20players%2C%20it%20seemed%20obvious%20that%20we%20should%20incorporate%20racket%20sports%20in%20our%20e-commerce%20business%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20so%20glad%20we%20did%2C%20because%20if%20we%20were%20selling%20kitchen%20utensils%20or%20candles%20or%20something%20we%20didn't%20know%20anything%20about%20or%20care%20much%20for%2C%20I%20doubt%20we'd%20still%20be%20plugging%20away%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-ecommerce-experiment-how-to-start-making-money-on-amazon-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20year%20of%20learning%20lessons%20and%20lackluster%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20we%20are.%20We%20believe%20in%20our%20product%2C%20and%20we're%20having%20fun%20trying%20to%20move%20inventory.%20Rather%20than%20feeling%20burned%20out%2C%20we%20feel%20energized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246c3ac68-4ce1-4343-b6e6-6b6bc0aae3c4%5C%22%3ESurround%20yourself%20with%20smarter%2C%20more%20experienced%20people%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFigure%20out%20what%20you%20want%2C%20identify%20someone%20who%20already%20has%20it%2C%20and%20ask%20them%20%E2%80%94%20politely%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20bit%20of%20their%20time.%20Then%2C%20ask%20questions.%20Get%20curious.%20This%20is%20good%2C%20general%20life%20and%20business%20advice%20that%20frequently%20comes%20up%20in%20interviews%20with%20people%20across%20all%20industries.%20I%20never%20tire%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20try%20to%20do%20everything%20on%20your%20own%20when%20you%20can%20potentially%20learn%20from%20someone%20else's%20mistakes%20and%20fast-track%20your%20path%20to%20success%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20seeking%20out%20mentors%2C%20put%20yourself%20in%20the%20same%20room%20%E2%80%94%20virtual%20or%20physical%20%E2%80%94%20as%20people%20with%20similar%20goals.%20I've%20heard%20it%20over%20and%20over%20again%3A%20%3Cem%3EWho%20you%20hang%20around%20matters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNetworking%20event%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bconference%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20sound%20particularly%20fun%20or%20exciting%2C%20especially%20to%20an%20introvert.%20Despite%20reporting%20on%20the%20benefits%20of%20attending%20such%20events%2C%20I%20had%20never%20bought%20in%20%E2%80%94%20until%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20when%20I%20spent%2010%20hours%20at%20a%20conference%20for%20real%20estate%20investors%20pursuing%20financial%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-conference-main-takeaways-review-should-i-attend-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20about%20what%20it%20was%20like%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20in%20a%20room%20with%20hundreds%20of%20like-minded%20investors%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20mentioning%20three%20main%20takeaways%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20you%20learn%20%E2%80%94%20from%20people%20who%20are%20more%20successful%20than%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20you%20connect%20%E2%80%94%20with%20people%20who%20could%20become%20your%20business%20partner%2C%20mentor%2C%20or%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%2C%20you%20gain%20momentum%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20just%20enough%20to%20inspire%20a%20key%20pivot%2C%20or%20take%20your%20first%20step%20into%20business%2C%20or%20simply%20keep%20the%20fire%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df56904a-8293-45c9-9361-c3b0143675a6%5C%22%3EWhen%20people%20tell%20you%20you're%20going%20to%20fail%2C%20use%20it%20as%20fuel%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20an%20underdog%20story.%20Who%20doesn't%3F%20I%20appreciate%2